                    <article class="servicebox04">
                        <h2> <i class="fa-solid fa-fan">
                            편의시설 및 서비스 안내
                        </i> </h2>
                        <div class="service service01">
                            <h3> 편의시설 안내 </h3>
                            <div class="guide guide01">
                                <img src="/img/guide_t04_img01.gif" alt="편의점" style="width: 60px;">
